episodes.title: 'Cult' members who tried to kidnap a Senior Coroner in 'bizarre' plot are jailed for seven years
episodes.description:
A group of four people who turned up at a court with a set of handcuffs and demanded to know where the senior coroner was have been jailed for their roles in a conspiracy to kidnap and falsely imprison him.The defendants had turned up at the court on April 20 last year, entered a room where another coroner was conducting documentary inquests and demanded to know where Mr Brookes was and said they were shutting down the court. All four were members of a group called the Federal Postal Court, or the Court for the People, which had 'self-conferred' powers.
